<h2 class="headline first-child text-color">
<section id="DIY">
DIY weather station projects</section>
</h2>

<p>Arduino based:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/Benjamin3992/OpenWeatherDuino">Openweathermap + Arduino = OpenWeatherDuino</a>
<p>An Arduino based standalone Open Source Weather Station which is connected to Openweathermap.org</p>
<li><a href="http://www.instructables.com/id/Wireless-outdoor-Arduino-weather-station-with-PC-l/">Wireless outdoor Arduino weather station</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.toptal.com/c/how-i-made-a-fully-functional-arduino-weather-station-for-300">Fully-functional Arduino weather station</a></li>
</ul>

